            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p>股權披露顯示，瑞銀於3月6日增持平保<a class=\"color_mpf\" href=\"stock1.php?code=2318\"><strong>（2318）</strong></a>1830.78萬股，均價48.2151元，持股量由9.79%升至10.03%。</p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"/>\n</p>\n<p></p> </div></div>\n</div>",
