            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p>股權披露顯示，The Capital Group Companies, Inc.於3月10日增持攜程<a class=\"color_mpf\" href=\"stock1.php?code=9961\"><strong>（9961）</strong></a>166.24萬股，均價496.1961元，持股量由8.9%升至9.14%。</p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"/>\n</p>\n<p></p> </div></div>\n</div>",
